      <akn:section eId="sec_31_3171_07">
        <akn:num>31-3171.07</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Advisory board.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-3171_07_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>In addition to the executive board, there shall be a standing advisory board consisting of 9 members, who shall be residents of the District.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-3171_07_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The executive board may create additional advisory boards as it considers appropriate.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-3171_07_c">
      <akn:num>(c)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The executive board shall solicit the recommendations of, and consult with, the advisory boards on:</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-3171_07_d">
      <akn:num>(d)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The executive board shall:</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-3171_07_e">
      <akn:num>(e)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p></akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-3171_07_f">
      <akn:num>(f)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Each person appointed to an advisory board shall have demonstrated and acknowledged expertise on issues related to at least one of the following groups:</akn:p></akn:content>
